;font-size: 14px\">2、</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">店主可拥有自己的微店及管理权限；</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">3、</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">不同等级</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的店主</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">享受不同的收益</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">；</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">4、</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">自定义设置店主收益模式，成为店长条件与结算方式等。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:5px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:5px;margin-left:0;text-indent:0\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"></span></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', 'microShopProfile', '1553943320', '15113', 'https://pic.vslai.com.cn/upload/common/1554197104.png', '3', '0', '', '0', '6', '0', '[]', '0', 'https://pic.vslai.com.cn/upload/common/1563782164.png', 'https://pic.vslai.com.cn/upload/common/1563782285.png', '0');
